{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Notification: dir property","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/dir","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.Notification.dir"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API\">Notifications API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/Notification\"><code>Notification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Static properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/maxActions_static\"><code>maxActions</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/permission_static\"><code>permission</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/actions\"><code>actions</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/badge\"><code>badge</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/body\"><code>body</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/data\"><code>data</code></a></li><li><em><code>dir</code> </em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/icon\"><code>icon</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/image\"><code>image</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/lang\"><code>lang</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/renotify\"><code>renotify</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/requireInteraction\"><code>requireInteraction</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/silent\"><code>silent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/tag\"><code>tag</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/vibrate\"><code>vibrate</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Static methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/requestPermission_static\"><code>requestPermission()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/click_event\"><code>click</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/show_event\"><code>show</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Web Notifications</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/getNotifications\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.getNotifications()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/showNotification\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.showNotification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div>\n<p>The <code>dir</code> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a> interface indicates the text direction of the notification, as specified in the <code>dir</code> option of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/Notification\" title=\"Notification()\"><code>Notification()</code></a> constructor.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A string specifying the text direction. Possible values are:</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"auto\"><a href=\"#auto\"><code>auto</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>adopts the browser's language setting behavior (the default.)</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"ltr\"><a href=\"#ltr\"><code>ltr</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>left to right.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"rtl\"><a href=\"#rtl\"><code>rtl</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>right to left.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> Most browsers seem to ignore explicit ltr and rtl settings, and just go with the browser-wide setting.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following snippet fires a notification; a simple <code>options</code> object is created, then the notification is fired using the <code>Notification()</code> constructor.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">body</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Your code submission has received 3 new review comments.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">dir</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rtl\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> n <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Notification</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"New review activity\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"rtl\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://notifications.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-notification-dir","title":"Notifications API Standard"}],"query":"api.Notification.dir"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Notification.dir"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API/Using_the_Notifications_API\">Using the Notifications API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The dir read-only property of the Notification interface indicates the text direction of the notification, as specified in the dir option of the Notification() constructor.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2023-04-07T06:19:30.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/notification/dir","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/notification/dir/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/312081aabba3885b35a81107b3c2fc53428896c5","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"dir","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification","title":"Notification"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/dir","title":"dir"}],"pageTitle":"Notification: dir property - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}